snippet.title: Wrath of the Roothless - Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam - https://store.steampowered.com/app/2827490
Discord - https://www.discord.gg/cxZNW7nPJn

Wrath of the Roothless is coming to Steam and Itch on the 12th of March.

Experience a melee only roguelite where the odds are ever against you, hordes of enemies, and obstacles will provide challenge enough!
